  "3192410": {
    "name": "机影：夏夜梦寻",
    "steam_appid": 3192410,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【人与机器人的仲夏夜之梦】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作品是以未来赛博都市为背景的文字冒险游戏。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方1群：933454572</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事背景</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在西海岸闪烁的霓虹下，黄金市——一座由废墟堆砌而成的赛博奇迹伫立于此。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高墙切断了富庶的白与贫穷的灰，也割开了人类与机器的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演游戏男主<strong>朴博明</strong>，一名游走在规则边缘的“烁金”AI督察局副局长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当追踪AI机器人的“电子纹路”化作无形的枷锁，当反叛组织“陨铁”的战火点燃灰区，你却被困在了一场挥之不去的怪梦里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个甜美又凉爽的夏夜，带上你的助手机器人<strong>莳萝</strong>，在这光怪陆离的赛博迷宫中穿行。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>脚下是救赎的指引，还是复仇的陷阱？</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>当梦境剥落，你寻找的是真相，还是另一个谎言？</strong>   </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>角色介绍</strong>   </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>莳萝</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >男主的助手机器人，是莉优送给他的搬家礼物。虽然是高性能机器人，但是性格活泼，很喜欢浪漫幻想。爱好是Cosplay，认为通过扮演动漫里的角色可以快速学习人类社会的知识。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192410/extras/83bca99f3a3f19c648d7a5bb130fa5d1.avif?t=1771419341\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192410/extras_big/83bca99f3a3f19c648d7a5bb130fa5d1.avif?t=1771419341 width=800 height=1036 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>莉优</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黄金市历史上最年轻的女市长，来自首府宇枢市的大小姐，背景深厚。是男主的救命恩人。因主张对AI机器人采取强硬手段而闻名。看似很靠谱，但在感情问题上单纯到有些笨蛋，是个具有双面性的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192410/extras/2f362d940c31be198e973676dddaba74.avif?t=1771419341\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192410/extras_big/2f362d940c31be198e973676dddaba74.avif?t=1771419341 width=800 height=1036 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>薇</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >朴博明学生时代在灰区的初恋，在十年前灰区AI机器人暴动造成的意外事故中去世，经常在朴博明的梦中出现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192410/extras/cc8547e267e46451098f5747bc1ec773.avif?t=1771419341\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192410/extras_big/cc8547e267e46451098f5747bc1ec773.avif?t=1771419341 width=800 height=1036 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黑焰</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >出身法官家庭的叛逆少女，热爱二次元和cosplay，和男主与莳萝在漫展中相识。对现有的AI管控措施不满。身份成迷，疑似是AI叛乱组织“陨铁”的成员。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192410/extras/8ebc2b30700eb15c99c44ff271fe23d0.avif?t=1771419341\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192410/extras_big/8ebc2b30700eb15c99c44ff271fe23d0.avif?t=1771419341 width=800 height=1036 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>伊霜</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黄金市市长莉优的秘书，AI督察局参谋长。是莉优父亲派来协助她的助手，也是指引男主成为AI督察的导师。平时总是摆着一张严肃的脸，但实际上是个很幽默的人。私下做一些莉优不方便做的“脏活”，被誉为黄金市的“影子市长”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192410/extras/55031efe35b5f46c71303bd9765124cf.avif?t=1771419341\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192410/extras_big/55031efe35b5f46c71303bd9765124cf.avif?t=1771419341 width=800 height=1036 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>水橙</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黄金市AI督察局支队长，曾是男主战斗小队的成员。常年活跃在和非法AI机器人战斗的一线，两年前从位于宇枢市的AI督察总部调任到黄金市。不苟言笑，坚守AI督察的行为准则，但私下对待AI机器人态度较为宽容。虽然个子不高但是气场很强，给人不好相处的感觉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192410/extras/94ff373502d40e7e4aacc2d62abc40cb.avif?t=1771419341\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192410/extras_big/94ff373502d40e7e4aacc2d62abc40cb.avif?t=1771419341 width=800 height=1036 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
